    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p><strong>Requirements </strong>You are holding at least one Hallowed Bolt on hand</p>\n<hr />\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-tab-count:1\">            </span>You transform a Hallowed Bolt into a Timeslicer, which appears as a clock’s needle. A Timeslicer possesses identical statistics as the Hallowed Bolt used to make it. You then make a ranged strike, using it as a thrown weapon. On a successful hit, the target needs to make a Will saving throw as a hex is cast upon the target, attempting to slow their perception of time. On a critical hit, you treat the outcome of the saving throw as one degree of success lower.</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"> </p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Critical Success </span></strong><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin\">The target is unaffected.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Success</span></strong><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin\"> The target is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.xYTAsEpcJE1Ccni3]{Slowed 1}  for 1 round.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Failure</span></strong><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin\"> The target is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.xYTAsEpcJE1Ccni3]{Slowed 1} for 1 minute.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">Critical Failure </strong>The target is <span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin\">@Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.xYTAsEpcJE1Ccni3]{Slowed 2}</span> for 1 minute.</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"> </p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">When you cast with three actions, you can convert one additional bolt and make a Strike with it against a different creature in range. These attacks increase your multi attack penalty, but you do not increase it until all attack rolls have been made. Any bolts you do not attack with during your turn lose their power and become useless.</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin\"> </span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Heightened</span></strong><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin\">(6<sup>th</sup>): When you spend three actions to cast this spell, you can add an additional bolt, up to 3 timeslicers.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Heightened</span></strong><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin\">(9<sup>th</sup>): When you spend three actions to cast this spell, you can add two additional bolts up to 4 timeslicers.</span></p>"
    },
